# arrangedObjects

**Instance Property**

The tree controller’s sorted content objects.

## Declaration

```swift
var arrangedObjects: NSTreeNode { get }
```

## Discussion

The value of this property represents a proxy root tree node containing the tree controller’s sorted content objects. The proxy object responds to [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTreeNode/children] and [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTreeNode/descendant(at:)] messages. This property is observable using key-value observing.

## Arranging Objects

- **rearrangeObjects()**: Use this method to trigger reordering of the tree controller’s content.
